snippet.title: Housewives Blind Revealed Louis Vuitton RED FLAGGED WHO!  Here is why.
snippet.description:
This video explains the highly talked about Deux Mois blind about a Housewife red flagged at Louis Vuitton.  Turns out it wasn't the Housewife everyone thought it was!  I tell you the story, who it really was and show you the proof.  Then we discuss if the explanation given is true!  This is a fun one.  

DecaDish is a 10 minute or so gossip sesh where Dana unloads some gossip to contemplate.
